content:
just following up from this, i've made 2 PR's;
- event stream [`data_column_sidecar`](https://github.com/ethereum/beacon-APIs/pull/535) event which will help with gather metrics around p2p layer similar to how `block_gossip` and `blob_sidecar` events currently work
- a debug endpoint to [get current data column sidecars for a block](https://github.com/ethereum/beacon-APIs/pull/537). Mainly for debugging any issues in the future with the actual stored data columns of a node
